    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it the perfect companion for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and has been kept up nicely. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
