    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i is a meticulously maintained example of luxury and utility. Finished in Alpine White, the exterior retains a deep gloss; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch, the body is straight and free of any major dents. The interior features Mocha Dakota leather that remains soft and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All cabin technology, from the premium Harman Kardon sound system to the panoramic moonroof, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the inline-six engine runs smoothly, backed by a comprehensive service log showing regular oil changes and a recent brake fluid flush. The tires are in great shape with significant tread life remaining. This is a non-smoker, pet-free vehicle that offers a quiet, confident ride. It comes with two sets of keys and all original manuals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_5",
